reviewText:
There are only five episodes on this dvd that can be found on the main volumes.
The episodes on this disk are:
1. It's A Cat's World (also found on Spooky Tails)
2. Glenda & Odessa (also found on It's Showtime!)
3. Up A Tree (also found on Odie Oh!)
4. Nice To Nermal (also found on Best Friends Forever)
5. Jon's Night Out (also found on It's Showtime!)
There are no Garfield shorts either.
